    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change GCSE exams and grade students in the same way as 2020",
        "additional_details": "Now we have gone back to pre-COVID GCSE grading. During the pandemic it was easier and made students feel less stressed about exams.\r\n \r\nWe believe this will be better for the future of the children taking their GCSEs.",
        "background": "In 2020, due to COVID-19, GCSE students' results were decided using teacher predicted results or algorithm standardised results for each subject they took.",
